name: Cheese & Spinach Omelette Wrap + Snacks Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Cheese & Spinach Omelette Wrap: Whisk eggs and milk together in a medium bowl. Heat a medium non-stick frying pan over medium heat and spray with oil. Pour in egg mixture, swirl to coat and cook for 1-2 minutes or until almost set. Top half the omelette with the cheese. Fold omelette in half to enclose filling. Remove from pan and set aside to cool.

Place wrap on a clean work surface. Place spinach leaves down middle of wrap, then top with omelette. Roll firmly to enclose. Cut in half. Snack 1: Cut green beans and capsicum into sticks. Snack 2: Top yoghurt with kiwifruit. Snack 3: Pack salsa in a small tub.
